# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok federal prosecutors and defense attorney 's are giving their opening statements in the trial of a south florida family charged with treating a haitian teenage girl like a `` slave .
# ::alignments
(s / state-01
      :ARG0 (a / and
            :op1 (p / person
                  :ARG0-of (p2 / prosecute-01)
                  :mod (f / federal))
            :op2 (a2 / attorney
                  :mod (d / defend-01)))
      :ARG1 (o / open-01
            :ARG0 a
            :ARG1 (t / try-02
                  :ARG1 (f2 / family
                        :location (s2 / south
                              :part-of (s3 / state
                                    :name (n / name
                                          :op1 "Florida")))
                        :ARG1-of (c / charge-05
                              :ARG2 (t2 / treat-01
                                    :ARG0 f2
                                    :ARG1 (g / girl
                                          :mod (t3 / teenage)
                                          :mod (c2 / country
                                                :name (n2 / name
                                                      :op1 "Haiti")))
                                    :ARG2 (r / resemble-01
                                          :ARG1 f2
                                          :ARG2 (s4 / slave))))))))

                  :time (d / date-entity

      :manner (m / man
            :mod (m2 / match)))

# ::id 1941 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok rank group plc , the british owner of the hard rock cafe chain , said friday that it plans to sell its dvd business and split off its film production unit to concentrate on gaming , hotels and restaurants .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (g / group
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "rank"
                  :op2 "Group"
                  :op3 " plc")
            :ARG0-of (o / own-01
                  :ARG1 (c / chain
                        :mod (c2 / cafe
                              :mod (r / rock
                                    :ARG1-of (h / hard-04)))
                        :mod (c3 / country
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Britain")))))
      :ARG1 (p / plan-01
            :ARG0 g
            :ARG1 (a / and
                  :op1 (s2 / sell-01
                        :ARG0 g
                        :ARG1 (b / business
                              :mod (d / digital)
                              :poss g))
                  :op2 (s3 / split-01
                        :ARG0 g
                        :ARG1 (u / unit
                              :ARG0-of (p2 / produce-01
                                    :ARG1 (f / film))
                              :poss g)
                        :purpose (c4 / concentrate-01
                              :ARG0 g
                              :ARG1 (a2 / and
                                    :op1 (g2 / gaming)
                                    :op2 (h2 / hotel)
                                    :op3 (r2 / restaurant))))))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (f2 / friday)))

                                    :op1 (s3 / shoot-02
                                          :ARG1 p2)
                                    :op2 (k2 / kill-01
                                          :ARG1 p2)))))))

            :ARG1-of (c4 / cause-01

                        :ARG1 w))
            :time (d2 / date-entity
                  :weekday (t / thursday))))
